                   <node depth="18" type="StaticText" id="" name="Customers find the curtain rod to be of top-notch quality, easy to put together and install, and appreciate its appearance, noting it looks like expensive rods. Moreover, the rod is sturdy with strong brackets, offers excellent value for money, and functions well in various settings, particularly in kitchens. Additionally, customers like its adjustability, being able to add or subtract pieces to customize the length as needed. However, stability receives mixed reviews - while some say it prevents movement, others report it bends easily." value="Customers find the curtain rod to be of top-notch quality, easy to put together and install, and appreciate its appearance, noting it looks like expensive rods. Moreover, the rod is sturdy with strong brackets, offers excellent value for money, and functions well in various settings, particularly in kitchens. Additionally, customers like its adjustability, being able to add or subtract pieces to customize the length as needed. However, stability receives mixed reviews - while some say it prevents movement, " label="Customers find the curtain rod to be of top-notch quality, easy to put together and install, and appreciate its appearance, noting it looks like expensive rods. Moreover, the rod is sturdy with strong brackets, offers excellent value for money, and functions well in various settings, particularly in kitchens. Additionally, customers like its adjustability, being able to add or subtract pieces to customize the length as needed. However, stability receives mixed reviews - while some say it prevents movement, others report it bends easily." enable="true" accessible="true" selected="false" index="293" visible="false" x="40" y="19090" width="750" height="442" bounds="[40,19090][790,19532]" nid="8975245445PFPQ3F6" childcount="0" left="40" top="19090" right="790" bottom="19532"></node> 
